name: Magislayer Sorceress - Ren Koumei
effect:
2 "Magislayer" Monsters
This card can only be Fusion Summoned OR Special Summoned by an "Magislay" or "Magikill" card effect, and can't be Summoned by other ways. You can only Special Summon 1 "Magislayer Sorceress - Komei" per turn. You can Special Summon this card from your Extra Deck by sending 2 Spell/Traps you control to the GY (In this case, you don't use "Polymerization"). If this card is Special Summoned: You can set up to two "Magislay" or "Magikill" Spell/Traps from your Deck to your Spell/Traps Zone, at the end of the turn this effect was activated, destroy all Spell/Traps on the Field. (Quick Effect): You can return this card you control to the Extra Deck and if you do, you can Special Summon 1 non-Fusion "Magislayer" Monster from your Extra Deck. You can only activate this effect of "Magislayer Sorceress - Komei" once per turn.
